title: Club tags wont show?
body:
They were showing for me previously. Now they arent. Not my own, and not anyone else in game or in the lobby. 

I googled it and every single page says "click the club tag menu click the gear click show club tags"

[Well.....](https://i.gyazo.com/1a7541dcedfb0d1b83178085b84539c1.png)

Seems pretty check  marked to me.

replies.body: I do see that you're currently in a club, and I don't believe there's any issue right now being unable to see club tags.  Reach out to us in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so we can look into this with you individually.  We'll respond asap!
